name: Honey Blue
description: A global conglomerate, Honey Blue serves clients in various business domains such as Food, Energy, Water, organic farming, aviation, hospitality, healthcare, eco-tourism, education, logistics, property, financial services, mining, design & build and other sustainable projects. Honey Blue is a company of repute whose strength lies in: a solid balance sheet with major assets, a quality network of contacts and partners, recognized expertise with substantial market share in each of the sectors in which it operates, and a united, competent and balanced loyal team.
